@startuml
title Writing Practice Component and Action Diagram
left to right direction
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

package "App Shell" {
  [WritingPageClient]
}

package "Flow" {
  [writingPracticeFlow]
}

package "View Layer" {
  [WritingPracticeView]
  [SessionsList]
  [WritingEditorPanel]
  [SubmissionReviewPanel]
  [WritingFlashcardReview]
}

package "Server Actions" {
  [listWritingPracticeSessionsAction]
  [createWritingPracticeSessionAction]
  [getWritingPracticeSessionAction]
  [submitWritingPracticeAnswerAction]
  [deleteWritingPracticeSessionAction]
  [reviewWritingFlashcardAction]
  [detachWritingFlashcardAction]
}

package "Backend API" {
  [/GET sessions/]
  [/POST session create/]
  [/GET session detail/]
  [/POST answer submission/]
  [/DELETE session/]
  [/POST flashcard review/]
  [/DELETE flashcard detach/]
}

[WritingPageClient] --> [writingPracticeFlow]
[writingPracticeFlow] --> [WritingPracticeView]

[WritingPracticeView] --> [SessionsList]
[WritingPracticeView] --> [WritingEditorPanel]
[WritingPracticeView] --> [SubmissionReviewPanel]
[WritingPracticeView] --> [WritingFlashcardReview]

[writingPracticeFlow] --> [listWritingPracticeSessionsAction]
[writingPracticeFlow] --> [createWritingPracticeSessionAction]
[writingPracticeFlow] --> [getWritingPracticeSessionAction]
[writingPracticeFlow] --> [submitWritingPracticeAnswerAction]
[writingPracticeFlow] --> [deleteWritingPracticeSessionAction]
[writingPracticeFlow] --> [reviewWritingFlashcardAction]
[writingPracticeFlow] --> [detachWritingFlashcardAction]

[listWritingPracticeSessionsAction] --> [/GET sessions/]
[createWritingPracticeSessionAction] --> [/POST session create/]
[getWritingPracticeSessionAction] --> [/GET session detail/]
[submitWritingPracticeAnswerAction] --> [/POST answer submission/]
[deleteWritingPracticeSessionAction] --> [/DELETE session/]
[reviewWritingFlashcardAction] --> [/POST flashcard review/]
[detachWritingFlashcardAction] --> [/DELETE flashcard detach/]

note right of [WritingEditorPanel]
Draft mode only:
- show prompt
- collect answer
- show review count only
- hide flashcard cards
end note

note right of [SubmissionReviewPanel]
Submitted mode:
- show submitted answer
- show reference German text
- enable flashcard review
end note

note bottom of [writingPracticeFlow]
Suggested steps:
- loadSessions
- showSessions
- createSession
- loadSessionDetail
- submitAnswer
- rateFlashcard
- deleteSession
end note

@enduml
